text: Hermann Dür (born 23 June 1925) was a Swiss equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
